Summer Event














THE PURCHASE PERIOD FOR THE SUMMER EVENT HAD ENDED.
If you purchased a set of qualifying tires between June 15 and July 15, 2017, reward requests must be postmarked or submitted online no later than August 15, 2017 and received no later than August 31, 2017. 
If you have already submitted a reward claim with Cooper Tire, you can check the status of your reward below.


