The Adventurer A/T is a true all-terrain tire that provides an aggressive five-rib tread design with dynamic handling, dependable tread wear and confident all-season performance. Its tread compound is formulated with an optimal mix of all-terrain and road traction properties to provide consistent and dependable performance and grip, while its tread and siping pattern handles wet, dry and off-road conditions, providing dependable mileage and a quiet ride. The Adventurer A/T is suitable for today's SUVs and 1/2 ton trucks.

**Available at national select retailers only.

