The CS5 Touring tire is the newest addition to Cooper’s proven touring passenger tire line. This premium tire delivers remarkable all-season performance targeted for drivers of modern sedans and SUVs. It includes an innovative new Wear Square™, which is a visual tread wear indicator that provides a convenient way to gauge the amount of wear on the tread of the tire, giving an indication of when it is time to replace the tire.
