Tire Details






$
50
            	Reward


            	Discoverer LSX
        		™
        		*
            
The Discoverer LSX is an S-rated premium sport utility vehicle tire that provides enhanced wet traction and all-season performance for sport utility vehicles, crossovers, light trucks and some vans. This tire showcases four wide, notched circumferential grooves with a center rib that provides resistance to hydroplaning, while improving traction. Its deep-biting, zig-zag sipes enhance wet traction and winter performance on snow and ice. The LSX's siped semi-open shoulder design provides great wet and snow traction.
 
**Available at select national retailers only.
View Discoverer LSX Details 

