truck/SUV tires and wheels only.                 TireBuyer.com 						return policy                              Easy installation                     We've partnered with more 							than 8,500 professional installers nationwide - including the best 							tire shops in your area.                   Here's how it works:                   After you add tires/wheels to your cart, we'll show 							you the TireBuyer installers in your area.                     Choose an installer, and we'll deliver your order 							right to their shop.                      Many orders arrive in 1-2 business 							days. 						                     Once your order is at the installer, just go to the tire 							shop and have your new tires installed.                                 Want help? Call our in-house 							experts                     If you're 							not sure what size tire you need, or if you have other questions, 							just give us a call or chat with us. Our customer service team:                         Has over 150 years of collective experience in the tire 							industry                     Is located in our offices in Bellevue, Washington (near 							Seattle)                     Can assist you in English or Spanish                     Receives regular in-house training, as well as training 							from tire and wheel manufacturers                         Customer service hours                    Monday through Friday:                     8am - 10pm ET                    Saturday:                     9am - 7:30pm ET                    Sunday:                     Closed                                 About TireBuyer                     Hi, it's nice to meet you! 							Here are a few quick facts about us.                         TireBuyer is owned by American Tire Distributors (ATD), 							the largest tire distributor in North America.                     ATD has been in business for more than 80 years.                     We have more than 115 warehouses across the United States 							- at least one in almost every state.                     TireBuyer has partnered with more than 8,500 professional 							tire installation shops across the U.S.                     We have an A+ rating from the Better Business Bureau and 							we've won Bizrate's Circle of Excellence Award (based on 							customer reviews) for the past three years. 						                     We offer thousands of product and installer reviews on 							our website.                 







