Back to top







Overview



Cooper Cobra Radial G/T
Passenger All Season
If you’re into classic cars or American muscle cars, the Cooper Radial G/T has the look you want. And with a tread built for strong grip and long wear, then refined for a smooth, comfortable ride, it has the performance you want, too. Count on the Radial G/T to deliver long-lasting good looks and plenty of driving enjoyment. 
Features

Performance tread increases tire-to-road contact, promoting strong handling and durability 
Built tough for long tread life
Optimized tread pattern for a quiet ride












