                                    Tread Life Warranty: 
                                        Varies by size/speed rating/load index. Please see specific tire size.
                                    
Uniformity Warranty:  First 2/32 tread wear. No quantity limitation.
Workmanship Material Warranty:  Prorated after 2/32 tread wear.
Manufacturer's Hazard Warranty:  
Test Drive Warranty:  N/A
Manufacturer's Special Warranty:  Prorate Mileage if not worn down to 2/32 Using Miles Achieved and 32nds Used

