Tire Stickers Cooper Tire Lettering Kit - White - 4 of Each: 1.25 inch tall Temporary Peel & ...



                    If you are looking to determine what design is best for your vehicle or have an upcoming photo shoot, race or event, Peel and Stick is the affordable Tire Lettering solution for you. This short-term product is quick and easy to apply and ideal for short to medium term durability, specifically under                    
                     1,000 miles of driving.To avoid damaging your Tire Stickers, it is important the correct letter height for your tire is ordered. There are two methods of determining the proper fitment for your tire:1. Measure the sidewall surface with a ruler - Be sure to measure the sidewall, NOT the entire surface from tread to wheel.2. Generic Tire Sizing guidelines - Identify the aspect ratio or series (generally the middle number of the tire specification) and match it to the generic tire sizing guide below to determine your letter height. Tire Series Specification          MAX Recommended Letter Height                   20                                                   0.5                   25                                                   0.75                   30                                                   1.0                   35                                                   1.25                   40                                                   1.25                   45                                                   1.5                   50                                                   1.75                   55                                                   2.0When in doubt, it is safest to size the same height as the tire manufacturer's brand letters.  Anything larger may risk damage in cornering or standard driving conditions. Fits: Audi, BMW, Volkswagen, Mercedes Benz, MINI, Porsche.                





